query:
SELECT brand, COUNT(*) as count, 
  SUM(CASE WHEN description IS NOT NULL AND description != '' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as with_description,
  SUM(CASE WHEN specifications IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as with_specs
FROM products 
WHERE brand IN ('Daicel', 'Waters', 'Phenomenex')
GROUP BY brand
ORDER BY count DESC;
